    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a nice finish, though there are some minor surface scratches and typical road wear expected for its age. Inside, the interior is clean and shows only light wear on the seating surfaces. Mechanically, the car performs well and has a solid service history, offering a dependable and comfortable driving experience.",
