      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to the highest standards of preservation. This vehicle exhibits a pristine aesthetic and flawless mechanical profile, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every detail reflects a commitment to showroom-quality integrity, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this peerless acquisition.",
